name: Gayatri
description:
Secret Gayatri mantra, traditionally chanted at the rising sun over the ganges, for perhaps over five thousand years.
Om Bhuh Om Bhuvah Om Swaha
Om Mahah Om Janah Om Tapah Om Satyam |
Om Tatsavitur Varenyam 
Bhargo Devasya Dheemahi
Dhiyo Yonah Prachodayat |
Om Aapojyotiraso Mritam
Brahma Bhur Bhuvah Swaha Om
